    "Following Prasad et al. (2023), we report the reward score and success rate (%) for WebShop and success rate for TextCraft.",
    "In our analysis, we identified and categorized the primary error types encountered by the different methods.",
    "These error types are as follows:",
    "• Cascading Task Failure (CTF): The entire task fails due to the failure of intermediate subtasks, often as a result of error propagation.",
    "• Commonsense Knowledge Error (CKE):"
